data.name: sdsChildFees.SelectCommand
data.value: SELECT TBL_STUDENT_REVAL_CHILD.NUM_FK_PRN_NO AS PRNNo, SUM(TBL_STUDENT_REVAL_CHILD.NUM_REVALUATION_FEE) AS RevaluationFee, SUM(TBL_STUDENT_REVAL_CHILD.NUM_VERIFICATION_FEE) AS VerificationFee, SUM(TBL_STUDENT_REVAL_CHILD.NUM_TOTAL_FEE) AS TotalFee, dbo.GetCollegeName(Tbl_STUDENT_COURSE.Num_ST_COLLEGE_CD) AS CollegeName, dbo.GetShortCollegeName(Tbl_STUDENT_COURSE.Num_ST_COLLEGE_CD) AS ShortCollegeName, dbo.GetCourseShortName(Tbl_STUDENT_COURSE.Num_FK_CO_CD) AS CourseName, Tbl_COLLEGE_MSTR.Num_BankACNo AS BankAccountNo, Tbl_COLLEGE_MSTR.Chr_BankBranch_Code AS BankBranchCode, '' AS Copy, dbo.GetInstanceName(TBL_STUDENT_REVAL_CHILD.Num_FK_INST_NO) AS InstanceName, Tbl_STUDENT_INFO.Var_ST_NM AS StudentName FROM TBL_STUDENT_REVAL_CHILD INNER JOIN Tbl_STUDENT_COURSE ON TBL_STUDENT_REVAL_CHILD.NUM_FK_PRN_NO = Tbl_STUDENT_COURSE.Chr_FK_PRN_NO INNER JOIN Tbl_STUDENT_INFO ON TBL_STUDENT_REVAL_CHILD.NUM_FK_PRN_NO = Tbl_STUDENT_INFO.Chr_PK_PRN_NO INNER JOIN Tbl_COLLEGE_MSTR ON Tbl_STUDENT_COURSE.Num_ST_COLLEGE_CD = Tbl_COLLEGE_MSTR.Num_PK_COLLEGE_CD WHERE (TBL_STUDENT_REVAL_CHILD.Num_FK_INST_NO = @InstanceID) AND (TBL_STUDENT_REVAL_CHILD.NUM_FK_PRN_NO = @PRNNo) GROUP BY TBL_STUDENT_REVAL_CHILD.NUM_FK_PRN_NO, Tbl_STUDENT_COURSE.Num_ST_COLLEGE_CD, Tbl_STUDENT_COURSE.Num_FK_CO_CD, Tbl_COLLEGE_MSTR.Num_BankACNo, Tbl_COLLEGE_MSTR.Chr_BankBranch_Code, TBL_STUDENT_REVAL_CHILD.Num_FK_INST_NO, Tbl_STUDENT_INFO.Var_ST_NM

data.name: sdsRevaluationFees.SelectCommand
